":"拥有相同的代码：该代码是由\n    lambda\n    表达式在\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"make_withdraw"},{"body":"\n    的主体中指定的。","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FOOTNOTE_REF","id":"#footnote-link-1","body":"1","href":"/sicpjs/3.2.3#footnote-1"},{"body":" 我们在这里可以看到为什么","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"W1"},{"body":"和","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"W2"},{"body":"表现为独立的对象。对","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"W1"},{"body":"的调用引用了存储在E1中的状态变量","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"balance"},{"body":"，而对","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"W2"},{"body":"的调用则引用了存储在E2中的","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"balance"},{"body":"。因此，一个对象局部状态的改变不会影响另一个对象。\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FIGURE","captionHref":"/sicpjs/3.2.3#fig-3.10","captionName":"Figure 3.10 ","captionBody":[{"body":"\n\t    使用","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"const W2 = make_withdraw(100);"},{"body":"创建第二个对象。\n\t  ","tag":"#text"}]}]},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 3.10","id":"#ex-3.10","child":[{"body":"\n    在\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"make_withdraw"},{"body":"函数\n    中，局部变量","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"balance"},{"body":"作为\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"make_withdraw"},{"body":".\n    的参数而创建。我们也可以使用\n    单独地,\n    来创建局部状态变量，采用\n    我们可以称之为一个\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"EM","child":[{"body":"立即调用的 lambda 表达式","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"\n    如下所示：\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":8,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHQCY0oFA4GYCuAdgMYAuAlgPbGgC2AhgNYCmA+gO6XkAWAJgCdGnABSViPSowA27RvWolyASlABvHKG2hBrcoUF1RAI1mMyrUAF4AfKC06nz0AqXFyN+5pe-nlfFBTc0tQW2tXRWU1Hz84pzMZC1IrCMTkqwBaSPdyAG5HePi9AyNQdMsCor8AX1BWGQBnK1jqvxLDOgAiCUbCfHxKUkpWD1AiYn5Grqq25xrCopqVcUkqWXkojxUChZxSWkbPAHUARhsGFg5uPiERUVOABkednDPRAA4XvKA","body":"function make_withdraw(initial_amount) {\n    return (balanc